Cognate with {{cog|sco|shaw||to show}}, {{cog|stq|scoe||to look, behold}}, {{cog|nl|schouwen||to inspect, view}}, {{cog|de|schauen||to see, behold}}, {{cog|da|skue||to behold}}, {{cog|is|skygna||to spy, behold, see}}. Related to {{l|en|sheen}}.

